headline: Costco Teamsters vote to authorize US-wide strike, union says
summary: Teamsters said on Sunday its members at U.S. retailer Costco Wholesale voted in favor of a nationwide strike, as they entered a final round of talks to reach a new contract ahead of a Jan. 31...
